                    <p>Heure: 22h00</p>
                    <p>Immerse yourself in the ancestral culture of the Dogon at the Ogobagnam Festival, a vibrant celebration of millennia-old traditions. Watch mesmerizing traditional dances, colorful rituals, handicraft demonstrations, and captivating musical performances. Explore the quaint Dogon villages, meet the hospitable locals, and discover the secrets of their unique way of life. An unforgettable cultural event in the heart of the magnificent landscape of the cliffs of Bandiaga </p>
